024/03/kings_of_leon_2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kings-of-leon">Kings of Leon</a>以“Split Screen”的形式分享了他们即将推出的新专辑中的第二首单曲 - 听下面的曲目。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="36" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/kings-of-leon-cover-interview-2021-when-you-see-yourself-2893854"><b>NME</b>大读物 – Kings Of Leon： <b><i>“</i></b><b>我们很幸福，我们彼此相爱”</b></a></li></ul><p>这首歌是纳什维尔乐队第九张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-share-explosive-single-mustang-and-announce-album-can-we-please-have-fun-3591493">《Can We Please Have Fun》</a>的最新试听歌曲，该专辑将于 5 月 10 日发行（<a href="https://kingsofleon.lnk.to/CanWePleaseHaveFun_UK">在此处预订</a>）。乐队上个月放弃了主打单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-share-explosive-single-mustang-and-announce-album-can-we-please-have-fun-3591493">“Mustang”</a> 。</p><p>这首歌曲以内省的形式呈现了弗洛维尔夫妇，用有质感、闪烁的吉他支撑着沉思的副歌：“<i>这是生活中的想法/分屏上的启示吗？</i> ”</p><p> “我们喜欢这首歌。我们认为粉丝也会喜欢它。 “Split Screen”可能会让人们在听过《Mustang》后对专辑的深度有所了解，”乐队在谈到这首歌时说道。</p><p>在这里观看这首歌的歌词视频： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Kings Of Leon - 分屏（官方歌词视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dub4vob1qrE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leon-preview-new-single-split-screen-3609382">在最近接受<i>iHeart Radio</i>采访时</a>，主唱 Caleb Followill 还透露，“Split Screen”是他最期待现场演奏的“Can We Please Have Fun”中的歌曲。 “‘分屏’将是一个美好的浪漫时刻，”他说。</p><p>即将推出的专辑是 2021 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/kings-of-leon-when-you-see-yourself-review-2894039">《When You See Yourself》</a>的后续专辑，由新合作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-harpoon">Kid Harpoon 制作。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kings-of-leons-caleb-followill-completely-fulfilled-by-new-album-can-we-please-have-fun-3595001">弗洛维尔解释说，他对这张唱片感到“完全满足”</a> 。他还在一份声明中表示，这是“他参与过的最令人愉快的唱片”。</p><h2> 《我们能玩得开心吗》曲目列表： </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="37" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“芭蕾舞广播电台”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="37" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <strong>“彩虹球”</strong> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="37" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1